{"tid":1781684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"ABC 杯葛華為 挪威電信採用愛立信為5G主要供應商 逐步淘汰華為","createTime":"2019-12-13T10:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T05:23:21.000Z","uid":165683,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"86731c5f41a4ddb5e2ca36445cc417a95743227b","tid":1781684,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:41:09.000Z","msg":"挪威國有電信商「挪威電信」決定，選擇瑞典的愛立信作為挪威5G網絡的主要科技供應商，並縮減中國電訊設備商華為的參與。<br />\n<br />\n「挪威電信」是挪威最大電信供應商，並活躍於北歐其他地區及五個亞洲國家，為超過1億8000萬名客戶提供服務。行政總裁說，5G時代已經來臨，又指已經做了廣泛的安全評估，並考慮了網絡技術質量、創新、現代化等因素，決定引入新的合作夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n挪威電信表示，會在未來4至5年，逐步淘汰華為的網絡組件。<br />\n<br />\n愛立信的發言人說，對被選中感到非常自豪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497546-20191213.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497546-20191213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6qZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=eb90f295\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497546-20191213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=268c4362\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497546-20191213.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a49cbb4cff3f3c51ea31f29667d76177d9cdd81b","tid":1781684,"uid":165683,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"ABC Manufacture Anywhere But China"},{"pid":"260204d9b8357d6497c123a9f2f11068d87561e4","tid":1781684,"uid":301820,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:42:43.000Z","msg":"挪威三文魚，我買爆您<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06054b322206496d87cd6bd0799c827651675294","tid":1781684,"uid":165683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"260204d9b8357d6497c123a9f2f11068d87561e4","tid":1781684,"uid":301820,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:42:43.000Z","msg":"挪威三文魚，我買爆您<img src=\"/a